{"tid":1325131,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 說服家中藍絲 有無巴絲可以幫手","createTime":"2019-07-16T18:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T21:00:23.000Z","uid":281618,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f129509ec34b235d3b85ce8b5fc421c60861bbc3","tid":1325131,"uid":281618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:51:07.000Z","msg":"我屋企人一向係偏藍<br />\n以往我完全放棄同佢地溝通 完全不提政治野<br />\n一來因為唔想嘈交 二來自己辯論能力都麻麻<br />\n最近想同佢地傾 做緊資料搜集遂一反搏佢地既論點<br />\n但我唔係咁叻 有D問題真係唔太識答<br />\n我老豆話:<br />\n香港而家有簽移交協議既國家 都有D無法治既國家(如印尼 印度)<br />\n點解中國就唔得?<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴絲打 應該點反駁?<br />\n<br />\n另外 現有既移交協議有D咩野把關? 點樣突顯送中條例既問題?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851286eb401292d4a32122f2b768566ffbaedd9e","tid":1325131,"uid":281618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:54:44.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ca6b312e8773b63059b3e8bb76979942f7909d","tid":1325131,"uid":262545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:56:49.000Z","msg":"印度同埋印尼會唔會無啦啦搞鳩香港人？<br />\n特首會唔會輕易送香港人去嗰啲國家？"},{"pid":"2ad8bee45450ad76e348f8710b48d3eb4d2ac90c","tid":1325131,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:57:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔理衝唔衝 21去金鐘</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1da56cd6df4934f2833fae00e0c001fc17ee145","tid":1325131,"uid":281388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:58:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f25b414315a91ecbe337885cd2938266fac56ad","tid":1325131,"uid":66208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y93ZznH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY93ZznH.png&h=578698b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"200666ad23628335c488f68671f9f6f1db679473","tid":1325131,"uid":281618,"like":0